  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Required_resource_arm.Required_resource">
<p>
A representation of resources needed in order to achieve a specified objective. The role of a required resource is determined by classification.
</p>
<note number="1">
A required resource can be classified as a "Facility", "Test equipment", "Supervisor", etc.
</note>
</ext_description>
